reviewText: The director of "Kamikaze Girls" in an interview for that movie talked Fukada Kyoko's acting skill way up. May have been referring to her work in this mini-series. It's more 'gal pal' / 'woman empowerment' material, very well acted, very compelling.
I have been looking for this for a while now and although the subtitles suck, The quality of the DVDs are top notch. Love the series
